When i bought horses i made sure i had over 100 Cha with both chars ( i think 100 cha is the cap to buy and sell with vendors).<br>
From my experience with horses so far they have pros and contras.<br>
pro:<br>
-You med almost whole time while you are on the horse.<br>
-You get a safefall bonus.<br>
-Mobs have a harder time to hit you  when you just want to ride through a Zone but dont bother to fight the mobs.<br>
contra:<br>
-Horse poof when you enter Water that is to deep.<br>
-No way to spell interrupt(didnt found a way yet)<br>
-If you ride with full speed you cant stop at the spot where you would normaly stop when you run(horse need a bit time before it run out (1 sec))<br>
-makes it a bit harder to melee(once you start your horse you need to give it some time to stop see above)<br>
